   The door, "Speed", defaults to show the Registered User as me when
   [i]nfo selected!  So if you want it rego'd in your name,  just ask
   me,  call me or email me such a request...  or simply complete the
   "My Version" rego form  included in this archive.   Read this form
   for more information on what "My Version" all means, etc. Wow!? ;)

   The reason I do this is to know how much interest there are in all
   my MAXs doors I do, from the rego responses, or comments & emails!


